Enumeration.ToolTip:
White Balance Function Mode: 
1) Formula1: OutValue = InValue + (InValue-BlackLevel)*BalanceRatio/64 (Set 0 for 0dBGain); 
2) Formula2: OutValue =  (InValue-BlackLevel)*BalanceRatio/2048+BlackLevel (Set 2048 for 0dBGain.).

